# f5a Expo conventions

## Package manager

- Use **bun** / **bunx** (not npm / npx) for installs, scripts, and one-off CLIs.
- Examples: `bun install`, `bunx expo start`, `bunx sb-rn-get-stories`.

## Expo Router

- Routes live under **`src/app/`**, not `app/`.
- Do not add new screens at the repo-root `app/` path.

## Path aliases

- `@/*` maps to `./src/*` (see `tsconfig.json`).
- Import app code as `@/components/...`, not deep relative paths from distant folders when an alias fits.

## Storybook config folder

- React Native Storybook lives in **`.rnstorybook/`**, not `.storybook/`.
- Do not initialize or edit web-only `.storybook/` for RN stories.
